{"tid":1810861,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【拳擊】香港運動員海外賽奪金，在頒獎台做出抗爭手勢。","createTime":"2020-01-04T08:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T10:00:51.000Z","uid":7988,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"512850db9ffffe29c197c3d58e76e10c5597ac7f","tid":1810861,"uid":7988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:22:39.000Z","msg":"　「非常非常需要的一場勝利。這是香港久違了10多年的海外賽金牌。」<br />\n<br />\n亞洲拳擊聯合會（ASBC）在12月26-31日舉行馬來西亞檳城國際邀請賽，吸引數以百計來自馬來西亞、台北、新加坡、泰國、印度尼西亞、尼泊爾、東帝汶等地的拳擊好手參加，爭奪各量級獎牌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3796104/org/94742f74991bf9c0c55bc26b0526099d.jpg/O23l7tfxnIoG7ZJ1wFatFy7MZ4FF-TOn8jelHPI3pRw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3796104%2Forg%2F94742f74991bf9c0c55bc26b0526099d.jpg%2FO23l7tfxnIoG7ZJ1wFatFy7MZ4FF-TOn8jelHPI3pRw&h=03d8204f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在頒獎台上，香港運動員做出抗爭手勢。（圖片由受訪者提供）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3796103/org/2a677788ab3bcd56418f8cbe0e206d7d.jpg/t4NDDET8Eh7xQJdc73Swem0BU36L7tVED8P_ZQ_D_2U\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3796103%2Forg%2F2a677788ab3bcd56418f8cbe0e206d7d.jpg%2Ft4NDDET8Eh7xQJdc73Swem0BU36L7tVED8P_ZQ_D_2U&h=adc8f1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手勢代表運動中的訴求。（圖片由受訪者提供）<br />\n香港國際拳擊聯會（HKIBF）派出4名運動員：袁文俊（64kg） , 譚梓鋒（60kg）, 鄧創文 （56kg） 及林敬皓（56kg 青少年）出戰檳城盃。經過數日賽事，最終代表香港的拳擊運動員勇奪1金1銀1銅，為歷來出戰海外賽事最佳成績。<br />\n<br />\n其中曾五度羸得香港冠軍頭銜的袁文俊，在是次比賽中保持穩定發揮，在量級組別中脫穎而出，一一以RSC勝過對手，以全勝姿態為香港奪得久違多年的海外賽金牌，這是繼他在2002年亞青杯奪得銀牌後又一海外賽事獎牌。<br />\n<br />\n另一香港運動員林敬皓雖然年僅17歲，並只有短短兩年拳齡，但他首次代表香港出外比賽，便即獲得不俗成績。他不單在準決賽第二回合RSC馬六甲選手，更在決賽跟勁旅台北選手打得難分難解，甚至在第三回合令對方被裁判讀秒。可惜最終還是不敵台北選手，獲得一面青少年56公斤组別銀牌。<br />\n<br />\n早前在香港奧運資格賽跟曹星如交手的香港運動員鄧創文則在56公斤組別獲得一面銅牌。出賽60公斤級別的譚梓鋒不幸於初賽落敗，無緣獎牌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%AD%A6%E5%82%99%E5%BF%97/416962/%E6%8B%B3%E6%93%8A-%E6%B8%AF%E5%B0%87%E6%8F%9A%E5%A8%81%E6%AA%B3%E5%9F%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%82%80%E8%AB%8B%E8%B3%BD-1%E9%87%911%E9%8A%801%E9%8A%85%E5%89%B5%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%BD%E4%BA%8B%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E6%88%90%E7%B8%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25BF%2597%2F416962%2F%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2593%258A-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258F%259A%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%25AA%25B3%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E9%2582%2580%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25B3%25BD-1%25E9%2587%25911%25E9%258A%25801%25E9%258A%2585%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25B8%25BE&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDlUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=fc5e96c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%AD%A6%E5%82%99%E5%BF%97/416962/%E6%8B%B3%E6%93%8A-%E6%B8%AF%E5%B0%87%E6%8F%9A%E5%A8%81%E6%AA%B3%E5%9F%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%82%80%E8%AB%8B%E8%B3%BD-1%E9%87%911%E9%8A%801%E9%8A%85%E5%89%B5%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%BD%E4%BA%8B%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E6%88%90%E7%B8%BE</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港拳擊係咪得曹星如，其他無人講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dbf31179882c3185a6855503af055d7970bac1","tid":1810861,"uid":34514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:23:04.000Z","msg":"依家要多啲文宣呀! 有新玩法 仲有教學同示範tim!<br />\n<br />\n[行動]文宣都十八區開花 A4 label周圍貼 (更新:大量現成圖 即print 即貼!)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810856</a>"},{"pid":"cca2ea633df13181cc32553f00266a6866453ee4","tid":1810861,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:23:39.000Z","msg":"真運動員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd7bb21383e17c65cf1892c053024b5691658f6","tid":1810861,"uid":313072,"like":1